      ## Operating Modes & Autonomy Levels
      
      | Level                                    | Description                                                                              | Push Behavior                    |
      | ---------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
      | **Level 1: Guided** (User Present)       | Agent asks before each major change. User approves each commit.                          | Push with approval.              |
